data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUN (1/28) NOON-2PM. Beautiful SINGLE level home w/ luxury upgrades now available in BAINBRIDGE! This highly desirable community includes 3 parks and 2 community pools! The great room opens up to 12-foot ceilings w/cozy fireplace and built-ins. Chef's kitchen includes double ovens, upgraded cabinets with fantastic storage and a gorgeous over-sized quartz island. SEE AMENITIES LIST for ALL upgrades! The primary bedroom includes a walk-in tile shower, double vanity, large soaker tub & entrance to the back patio. Main level bonus room w/ barn doors can serve as 4th bedroom or office. Enjoy the beautiful Idaho evenings under the covered patio with extended pavement and pergola. This is a quiet, secluded lot. OWNED SOLAR POWER SYSTEM set up for home use & EV charging - no more power bill! Front extended driveway.
